@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Return Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>We want to ensure you have a satisfying experience with our products. Please review our return policy below:</p>
<div>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>Refund Eligibility:</strong> Customers are eligible for a refund within 7 days of the original purchase date.</li>
        <li><strong>Refund Process:</strong> To request a refund, please contact our customer support team with your order details.</li>
        <li><strong>Refund Method:</strong> Refunds will be credited back to the original payment method used for the purchase.</li>
        <li><strong>Exchanges:</strong> We do not offer exchanges for eBooks. Customers must request a refund for the original purchase and then repurchase the desired eBook.</li>
        <li><strong>Policy Changes:</strong> Our return policy is subject to change. Any updates will be communicated to customers.</li>
    </ol>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns regarding our return policy, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:ebookstore@gmail.com">ebookstore@gmail.com</a>.</p>
</div>

